      • initTourWithPOIs

        public static java.util.Map<Position,java.util.Set<Position>> initTourWithPOIs()
        sets a network of positions of a tour. Some of the positions are POIs and all the POIs are in the network. The three POIs are 04, 19, and 47. The departure is 02 and the arrival is 48. The network built in this example method is described in file src/main/resources/itineraries/network_for_itinerary_with_three_pois.txt.
